<br />
<br />i have tried all different kinds and can't find a brand that will work consistently.  sometimes they work, sometimes not (eg, mosel, sony, sanyo, sharp).  
<br />
<br />does it have it have anything to do with the ts-rom board # or wram chip?
<br />
<br />any help would be great!

		

		</td>
